A Personal data collected and used by
Huacheng
We collect several types of information from and about
        users of our Services, including information that you directly provide to us and it identifies you personally,
        such as, without limitation, name, postal address, e-mail address and telephone number.
We may also automatically collect certain information as
        you navigate through the website or use our Services, such as usage details, equipment profiles and IP
        addresses, by means of cookies, web beacons and other tracking technologies.
We have set out below, in a table format, a description of
        the ways we
may
use your personal data, and which of the legal bases we
        rely on to do so. We have also identified what our legitimate interests are where appropriate.
We will only collect the
personal data
that is necessary for its specified, concrete, explicit
        and legitimate purposes and not further processed in a manner that is incompatible with those purposes. You have
        the right to choose whether or not to provide the
data
we have requested, but in most cases, if you do not
        provide your personal
data
, we may not be able to provide you with our services or
        respond to your queries.
Note that we may process your personal data for more than
        one lawful ground depending on the specific purpose for which we are using your data. Please contact us if you
