2. Cookies and other technologies
Our website and apps use cookies and
        similar technologies. We use functional cookies to ensure that our website and services operate properly and
        analytical cookies to make your user experience optimal. Third-party cookies may collect data outside our
        websites as well. As you navigate through and interact with the website and our services, we may use automatic
        data collection technologies to collect certain information about your
equipment, browsing actions, and patterns,
        traffic data, logs and other communication data. You can find more information on our
Cookie Statement
.
Our Privacy Policy does not cover the use
        of cookies by others, including, without limitation, our partners, affiliates, tracking utility company and
        service providers. We do not have access or control over these cookies.
