        the consent of a parent or guardian. If a child's personal data is collected with prior parental consent, we
        will only use or disclose the data as permitted by law, with the explicit consent of the child's parents or
        guardians, or when necessary for the protection of the child.
Huacheng
strongly recommends that parents take an active role in
        supervising the online activities of their children. If you believe we might have any information from or about
        a child, please contact us at
