        data to third-party service providers and business partners and your
personal
        data
may be
transferred,
        stored and processed outside of the country or region where it was initially collected.
The applicable
        law in the countries and regions where we operate may differ from the laws applicable to your country of
        residence.
There are
        different risks under different data protection laws and that we may transfer and store your
personal
        data
to overseas facilities.
However, we
will take
necessary measures to ensure that your information is
        processed
as required by
        this Policy and
in conformity with the
        applicable laws and appropriate technical security measures are adopted to safeguard your privacy.
